Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.84,0:00:08.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Here I am again.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.84,0:00:13.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.64,0:00:15.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Fwap{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.76,0:00:18.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How many days of food expenses\Nwill we save from this?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.43,0:00:20.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is wonderful! Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.06,0:00:25.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We got extravagant for New Year's,\Nso she told us to be frugal for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.81,0:00:29.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But now we can have delicious food\Nfrom tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.24,0:00:31.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Warm\NWarm
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.15,0:00:36.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We were already done eating.\NThose are the leftovers, so I hope that's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.16,0:00:41.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}D-Delicious!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.83,0:00:44.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Th-The egg rice is delicious!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.58,0:00:50.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Rei. Can you sleep with Momo tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.13,0:00:52.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's a good idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.59,0:00:54.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do that! After all, tomorrow's Saturday.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.89,0:00:59.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have to go home tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.60,0:01:02.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Let's stay here together!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.35,0:01:07.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Why, why, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.82,0:01:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Momo.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.53,0:01:24.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've got a match coming up\Nthat I just can't lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.58,0:01:28.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So I have to go home and study.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.63,0:01:31.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Study? Do you have a test?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.09,0:01:34.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.26,0:01:41.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}It's a test where I show my opponent\Nand myself how hard I've been trying.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.35,0:01:45.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Momo.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.40,0:01:49.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then you have something to tell Rei.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.11,0:01:50.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tell him what?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.23,0:01:53.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Rei says he has a test.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.24,0:01:57.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right. So what do you say at a time like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.62,0:02:00.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You say, "Do your best."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.75,0:02:08.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Rei, do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.88,0:02:10.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.75,0:02:14.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I'll do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.58,0:04:07.99,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Black River (Part 2)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.16,0:06:09.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.74,0:06:11.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...time to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.64,0:06:35.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After that, I spotted Kiriyama\Njust once at the Shogi Hall.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.06,0:06:44.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He was looking at shogi game records\Nand making copies of them.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.90,0:06:46.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was going to talk to him, but...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.78,0:06:51.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I saw that stern look on his face,\Nand stopped.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.79,0:07:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kiriyama had been gathering the game records\Nfor Shimada 8th-Dan, and Gotou 9th-Dan.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.54,0:07:03.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just those two.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.46,0:07:06.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh. The little punk.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.38,0:07:10.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Man, that pisses me off. What a jerk.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.18,0:07:13.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's totally ignoring the possibility\Nthat I could win?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.14,0:07:17.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And he expects to crush Mr. Shimada,\Nthen move right on to Gotou?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.10,0:07:18.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Who does he think he is?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.02,0:07:25.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't have it. A vision of me beating Gotou\Nand then facing off against Mr. Shimada.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.28,0:07:28.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I understand.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.82,0:07:31.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.28,0:07:33.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's what the problem is.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.83,0:07:38.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The vision Kiriyama sees isn't just\Na selfish figment of his imagination.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.87,0:07:42.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We're professionals.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.54,0:07:44.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whether I accept it or look away,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.71,0:07:49.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}deep down I measure my own ability\Nwith cruel precision.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.76,0:07:55.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Measuring that is what it means\Nto be a professional.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.64,0:07:58.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There are some people who think, "I may win"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.44,0:08:04.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and there is a possibility that they will win.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.94,0:08:09.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't have it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.57,0:08:14.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A vision of me beating Gotou\Nand then facing off against Mr. Shimada.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.37,0:08:17.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And that's how it is.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.83,0:08:26.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But going from there, trudging on\Nand sidling up to victory{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.38,0:08:29.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}is also part of a professional's job.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.26,0:08:34.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Gotou often uses the forms of Static Rook\Nand Bear in the Castle.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.89,0:08:37.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In response, I'll use the Windmill.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.56,0:08:39.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If Gotou is "heavy" and "stiff"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.43,0:08:42.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll be "light" and "expansive".{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.37,0:08:58.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, please begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.91,0:09:00.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have a good game.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.59,0:09:52.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is my second time playing against Gotou.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.72,0:09:58.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Last time, to prepare for a drawn-out battle\Nfrom Gotou's heavy defensive position,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.64,0:10:01.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I also strengthened the defense\Naround my king,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.56,0:10:06.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but the "nimbleness" I always put my faith in\Nwas weakened by the armor it wasn't used to{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.44,0:10:08.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and the result was a crushing defeat.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.74,0:10:24.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Based on that, I've come up\Nwith a number of countermeasures.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.12,0:10:30.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This time, I've decided to face him\Nwith what I excel at.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.84,0:10:35.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I won't shield my king much,\Nbut I'll move the pieces around quickly,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.51,0:10:39.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}making countless small wounds,\Nand stealing his vitality.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.43,0:10:44.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Against that...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.73,0:10:49.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Gotou will make a firm, measured defense,\Nand attack me with a single massive strike.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.19,0:10:52.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If that strike hits me, it's over.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.90,0:10:56.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't let my concentration slip one millimeter.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.82,0:11:00.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I'm ready to do this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.28,0:11:04.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A match in which victory and defeat\Nis decided 100% beforehand{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.83,0:11:09.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}doesn't exist between professionals.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.75,0:11:14.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Such unpleasant clouds, like it'll rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.88,0:11:18.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, on the news\Nthey were saying it'll snow tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.01,0:11:20.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No wonder.\NI thought it was especially cold out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.15,0:11:40.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just how much vitality does he have?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.91,0:11:42.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I keep wounding him, but he won't crumble.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.33,0:11:45.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There are no openings to attack.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.62,0:11:49.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've drawn a lot of blood,\Nbut he hasn't flinched.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.08,0:11:56.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Conversely, my moves\Naren't getting very far right now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.22,0:12:06.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And then...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.31,0:12:08.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...that one strike came.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.73,0:12:15.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sacrificing his Rook for my Silver?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.58,0:12:28.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What the hell is he doing?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.00,0:12:37.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What is...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.13,0:12:39.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...this man seeing?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.63,0:12:42.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's attacking me with tremendous force.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.18,0:12:44.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He'll pry me open!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.97,0:12:47.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Pitch black water is rushing in.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.97,0:12:49.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't breathe...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.56,0:12:52.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just like that, I'm getting dragged down...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.81,0:12:54.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...to the bottom.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.56,0:12:58.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's nothing I can do.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.41,0:13:07.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.33,0:13:12.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You were light.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.42,0:13:17.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But still a little heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.21,0:13:23.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After I moved 2-f-Bishop,\Nyou defended with 5-b-Gold from the left.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.63,0:13:26.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You should've gone up to 6-c-Gold instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.05,0:13:30.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The way you did it, the "heaviness" came out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.02,0:13:33.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lightness is your creed, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.64,0:13:34.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If so...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.65,0:13:37.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...don't hesitate.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.53,0:13:44.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That was pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.78,0:13:48.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not only was it a helpless, complete defeat,\Nbut my delusions were shattered as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.41,0:13:54.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A full course, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.25,0:13:55.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't hesitate.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.58,0:13:58.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's the deal with that heavy manliness?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.59,0:14:00.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How old is he? 41?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.71,0:14:04.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Will I be able to project\Nthat kind of punch in ten years?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.43,0:14:07.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I bet he's popular with the ladies.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.05,0:14:09.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now I'm getting pissed off.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.01,0:14:14.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right. For the rest of the night...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.27,0:14:20.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Course A. If it goes in, I drink my cares away\Nat the usual hostess pub.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.23,0:14:24.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Course B. If I miss, I go home,\Nget under the covers, and sob.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.75,0:14:38.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Rustle Rustle Rustle{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.30,0:14:42.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Gasp!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.68,0:14:49.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Shiver\NShiver\NShiver
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.97,0:14:51.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.22,0:14:53.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps a Course C?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.06,0:14:54.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Shrink\NShrink
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.06,0:14:54.81,LeftSignM2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Course C:\NBring a stray cat\Nhome and\Ntake care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.02,0:14:55.60,DefaultLow2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mew...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.14,0:14:57.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What should I do?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.48,0:15:04.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, already! I get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.28,0:15:10.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, okay. Stop crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.78,0:15:13.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We'll start again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.91,0:15:16.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You and me both, from square one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.00,0:15:19.00,Next Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Black River (Part 2)
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.80,0:15:27.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.76,0:15:30.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You look well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.47,0:15:33.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.81,0:15:37.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.14,0:15:43.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If we keep going like this,\Nyou and I will go head to head.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.94,0:15:46.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm looking forward to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.28,0:15:49.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It should be a little more interesting\Nthan beating you with my bare hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.28,0:15:53.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.99,0:15:57.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to pass on a message\Nto your old man, Kouda.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.75,0:16:00.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's about that stalker woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.88,0:16:04.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tell him to get her off my back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.25,0:16:07.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She's really annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.96,0:16:08.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You know?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.26,0:16:12.76,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Beyond the Door
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.26,0:16:12.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He was provoking me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.80,0:16:14.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I know that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.39,0:16:18.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.23,0:16:20.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have to do it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.90,0:16:24.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}First, I have to deal with today.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.11,0:16:28.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nothing will start unless I win today.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.99,0:16:34.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kai Shimada, 8th dan. Five years in Rank A.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.91,0:16:39.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've been looking at a lot of his game records,\Nbut it's strange.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.50,0:16:41.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't find any distinctive features.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.92,0:16:44.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tactics he's good at, his weaknesses...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.21,0:16:48.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's nothing I can pinpoint.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.99,0:17:16.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I haven't played against him before.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.45,0:17:18.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But, wait...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.41,0:17:25.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When I was in grade school,\Nhe was a guest speaker{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.79,0:17:28.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}at a children's shogi tournament I attended.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.55,0:17:32.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He was awfully thin and tall,\Nand I remember he spoke quietly.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.55,0:17:36.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'd had a winning streak,\Nso I just watched from afar.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.72,0:17:39.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He didn't really make an impression on me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.93,0:17:43.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Instead of "playing to win,"\Nhe's someone who "plays not to lose" shogi.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.60,0:17:50.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Matches against people like that\Nare usually drawn-out battles.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.57,0:17:53.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's not my favorite.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.99,0:17:58.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.75,0:18:05.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't get irritated.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.00,0:18:07.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's where he'll eat me alive.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.63,0:18:09.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Stay calm.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.88,0:18:14.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Gotou recently gave it to me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.01,0:18:17.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can not lose here.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.60,0:18:23.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No matter what.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.01,0:18:59.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I went first for this match.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.47,0:19:01.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's a Double Fortress.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.76,0:19:03.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's been standard moves up to now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.97,0:19:06.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All right, time to start the battle.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.14,0:19:08.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Here I go.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.06,0:19:46.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}5-b-Rook?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.27,0:19:50.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Does he intend to block everything?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.23,0:19:52.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In that case...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.82,0:19:58.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He moved his Gold back.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.49,0:20:03.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Does he mean to move the Rook around?\NThen so will I.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.79,0:20:13.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Somehow...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.34,0:20:18.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...it's hard for me to move.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.72,0:20:22.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}At a time like this,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.05,0:20:24.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}it's a good idea...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.81,0:20:27.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}to surround the king.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.19,0:20:31.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Surround...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.36,0:20:34.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wait a second.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.98,0:20:37.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Something's wrong.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.90,0:20:41.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was supposed to be attacking.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.70,0:20:43.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And yet...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.33,0:20:48.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...somewhere along the way, I started defending?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.66,0:20:51.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What is this?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.46,0:20:54.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When did the situation get this bad?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.00,0:20:57.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I didn't... make any mistakes.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.21,0:20:59.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No mistake, and yet...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.47,0:21:01.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And yet, what is this?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.05,0:21:02.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.68,0:21:05.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This intensity?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.89,0:21:13.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.73,0:21:16.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...attack anymore?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.94,0:21:20.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Crap!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.45,0:21:27.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gold General
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.45,0:21:27.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Knight
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.83,0:21:38.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Geez. You finally look this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.71,0:21:42.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Shogi Hall
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.38,0:21:44.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.56,0:21:50.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What did you come here for, kiddo?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.97,0:21:53.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have a match today.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.14,0:21:54.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Big Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.56,0:21:55.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How's your fever?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.90,0:21:57.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You still have one.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.56,0:22:01.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You need to take care.\NYour promotion is on the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.36,0:22:05.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You promised you wouldn't overdo it,\Nremember? To both your teacher and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.28,0:22:07.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In exchange, we promised\Nwe wouldn't tell anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.95,0:22:10.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I'll head home and lie down.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.04,0:22:12.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.16,0:22:14.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.54,0:22:17.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for getting on your case like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.88,0:22:20.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I was just surprised to see you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.63,0:22:22.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So why are you here, kiddo?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.09,0:22:25.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is there something you wanted to tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.80,0:22:27.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Actually, Big Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.85,0:22:30.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.06,0:22:34.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to split Kiriyama's head in half.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.39,0:22:37.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dang it, kiddo...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.19,0:22:42.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was wondering what you were going to say.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.07,0:22:47.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}Such a troublesome thing...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.03,0:22:52.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.58,0:22:57.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's continue, shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.04,0:23:00.04,Next Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Beyond the Door
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.01,0:24:32.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.01,0:24:36.18,EpNum,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 14
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.51,0:24:36.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can't be eating cold food\Nwhen you're depressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.18,0:24:38.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You'll lose half of your hit points.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.98,0:24:41.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is that how it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.39,0:24:44.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?\NI can't understand it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.07,0:24:50.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's try advancing it from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.11,0:24:52.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"March Comes in Like a Lion"!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.24,0:24:56.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,At long last, my Big Brother appears!\NYou'll watch our brotherly love, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.45,0:24:58.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Big Brother!
